Howard Stern Show
April 13, 2009

Uploaded By:  wushdishmeen
REMEMBER THE NAME



Unfortunately,  the Howard Stern Show is on vacation this week.  The good news is that all this week they are airing "Fight Week" which features all of the fights that occurred between Stern staffers in the past now uncensored and uncut.  This should hold you over until next week when hopefully they are back live.
